body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Kids & Youth             Kids & Youth      Hey kids, want to be a web ranger?  As a WebRanger you will have one important job: to have fun while learning new things. You will solve mysteries and puzzles, play games, take part in stories, and gather secret words.  Children's Corner -  A History E-Library for children provided by the National Park Service
title: Canaveral National Seashore: Kids & Youth
